10:14 AM Defendant Freddy R Huber in court.  Attorney Dominic Richards in court for Freddy R Huber.  Attorney Jonathan Ross in court for State of Wisconsin. Rights/ Elements.  Defendant pleads guilty to counts 2, 3, and 4. Judgment to be entered. Count 1 dismissed. On counts 3 and 4 Court found defendant guilty and entered judgment. Court withhold sentence and places defendant 24 months probation. For count 3, $443 cost/ fines. For count 4, $243 cost/ fines, AODA, any treatment recommendations by the DOC, and DNA Sample.
